thread.title_full: YesStyle.com reviewed by Diane Yeh LAc Eamp

author: Diane Yeh LAc Eamp
title: Diane Yeh LAc Eamp
text: I've enjoyed this site for it's up to date fashion trends in Asian & Europe which is super late in the United States. Even though the shipping of the merchandise takes a while but I guess the free international shipping make up for this deficit. However, this is my first time order on this site so if I could I would give another review update to give a more accurate review of the whole transaction from ordering until delivery.
